OL,3,CUK at risk of 'lost generation' amid
OL,4,Crising youth unemployment
OL,6,FThe number of people in the UK who are
OL,7,Fnot in education, employment or
OL,8,Ftraining (Neet), could reach 1.25
OL,9,Fmillion within the next five years,
OL,10,Frisking a 'lost generation', according
OL,11,Fto a new report.
OL,13,FCurrently one in eight people aged 16
OL,14,Fto 24 in the UK are Neet, but this
OL,15,Fcould rise to one in six young people
OL,16,Fby 2031, the government-commissioned
OL,17,Freview found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
