OL,3,CUK at risk of 'lost generation' amid
OL,4,Crising youth unemployment
OL,6,FFormer Labour health secretary Alan
OL,7,FMilburn, who is leading a review of
OL,8,Fthe Neets crisis for the government,
OL,9,Fwill publish his interim report on
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,12,F"Detachment is no longer temporary,"
OL,13,FMilburn said ahead of the publication.
OL,15,F"For too many young people it is
OL,16,Fbecoming permanent. We are at risk of
OL,17,Fa lost generation."
OL,26,@yD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
