OL,3,CUK at risk of 'lost generation' amid
OL,4,Crising youth unemployment
OL,6,FEntry level jobs have been in sharp
OL,7,Fdecline, with 1.6 million fewer low
OL,8,Fand medium skilled jobs in the
OL,9,Feconomy, making it difficult for
OL,10,Fpeople to get into the jobs market,
OL,11,Fhis report will show.
OL,13,FVacancies in hospitality have halved
OL,14,Fin the last four years alone, while so-
OL,15,Fcalled "Saturday jobs" have long been
OL,16,Fdeclining and apprenticeships have
OL,17,Fplummeted 35% in the past decade.
OL,26,@wD@HOUwD@VO]
