OL,3,CUK at risk of 'lost generation' amid
OL,4,Crising youth unemployment
OL,6,FThe Milburn Review found that six in
OL,7,F10 people young people had never had a
OL,8,Fjob, with anxiety linked to social
OL,9,Fmedia also driving economic inactivity
OL,10,Famong the age group.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
