OL,3,CUK at risk of 'lost generation' amid
OL,4,Crising youth unemployment
OL,6,FThe most recent figures showed 12.8%
OL,7,Fof all people aged 16 to 24 in the UK
OL,8,Fwere Neet in October to December 2025,
OL,9,Fwith the total number 957,000,
OL,10,Faccording to the Office for National
OL,11,FStatistics.
OL,13,F"The first rung of the career ladder
OL,14,Fhas thinned. For too many young people
OL,15,Fit is now simply out of reach,"
OL,16,FMilburn said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
