CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780052575
OL,3,CUK at risk of 'lost generation' amid
OL,4,Crising youth unemployment
OL,6,F"That places them in a hopeless Catch-
OL,7,F22 where employers ask for work
OL,8,Fexperience but the opportunities for
OL,9,Fyoung people to gain it have narrowed
OL,10,For gone."
OL,12,FMilburn is expected to call for urgent
OL,13,Faction from the government and say the
OL,14,Fissue "should be the priority" as too
OL,15,Foften young people are heading for a
OL,16,F"life not in jobs, but on benefits".
OL,18,FA survey of Neets found 84% said they
OL,19,Fwanted a job or training, which
OL,20,Fchallenges the narrative that young
OL,21,Fpeople do not want to work.
OL,26,@rD@IO]vD@GOUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
