PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780052575
OL,3,CUK at risk of 'lost generation' amid
OL,4,Crising youth unemployment
OL,6,FThe research also found that for every
OL,7,F#1 spent on employment support for
OL,8,Fyoung people, around #25 was spent on
OL,9,Fbenefits, which it describes as a
OL,10,F"fundamental imbalance in how public
OL,11,Fmoney is spent".
OL,13,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,14,FMcFadden, who commissioned the report,
OL,15,Fpreviously said the impact of youth
OL,16,Funemployment could scar people for the
OL,17,Frest of their lives, branding it a "a
OL,18,Fquiet crisis, a ticking timebomb".
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@OO]yD@dOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
