CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780052575
OL,3,CUK at risk of 'lost generation' amid
OL,4,Crising youth unemployment
OL,6,FHe is expected to announce plans for
OL,7,F300,000 extra work experience
OL,8,Fplacements over the next three years.
OL,10,FMcFadden pledged to "work across
OL,11,Fgovernment and with employers,
OL,12,Fcharities and young people to drive
OL,13,Freal change, so more young people are
OL,14,Fearning or learning, not left behind".
OL,16,FMarks & Spencer chief executive Stuart
OL,17,FMachin said the report "lays bare the
OL,18,Fjoblessness crisis facing a generation
OL,19,Fof young people", warning that the
OL,20,Ffindings were "shocking but not
OL,21,Fsurprising".
OL,26,@rD@UOUvD@eO]yD@XOU{D@PO]|D@OOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
