OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780052575
OL,3,CUK at risk of 'lost generation' amid
OL,4,Crising youth unemployment
OL,6,FWhile Big Issue founder and crossbench
OL,7,Fpeer in the House of Lords, John Bird,
OL,8,Fsaid it would be those "disadvantaged
OL,9,Fby poverty who lose out" when the job
OL,10,Fmarket becomes more competitive.
OL,12,F"If the Milburn Review is serious
OL,13,Fabout a system reset, it must start by
OL,14,Frecognising poverty is not just an
OL,15,Foutcome of the Neet crisis ` it is its
OL,16,Fdriving force," Bird said.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
